Usage: addNetToNetGroup [-help] <netGroupName> -net {netName | netNameList}

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
<netGroupName>                        # Specifies the name of the created net
                                      # group. (string, required)
-net {netName | netNameList}          # Specifies the name of an individual
                                      # net, bus, or segment of a bus or list
                                      # of nets. (string, required)